T02TD3091E:187b-1: gnas yid dang mthun zhing bkra shis par gro ga'am ras la gzungs 'di bris te /
T02TD3091E:187b-2: gdugs kyi rgyal mtshan gyi rtse mo la btags pa'am /
T02TD3091E:187b-3: yang na rin po che'i sgrom du bcug ste /
T02TD3091E:187b-4: mandal gyi dbus su bzhag nas sam dngos grub kyi rten pa dmar ser gyi zho'am /
T02TD3091E:187b-5: mar khu'am yang na chang ngam /
T02TD3091E:187b-6: zan la sogs pa bzhag nas lha'i rnal 'byor byas te gsol ba btab la /
T02TD3091E:187b-7: tshangs pa dang dbang po la sogs pa la gtor ma sbyin te /
T02TD3091E:187b-8: yang gsol ba btab nas dngos grub gsol bar dmigs te bsgom zhing bzlas par bya'o //
T02TD3091E:187b-9: de nas nam zhig na du ba dang /
T02TD3091E:187b-12: zos na tshe ring ba dang /
T02TD3091E:188a-2: yang na bu 'dod pa gang la las gzungs 'di bris te /
T02TD3091E:188a-3: gdugs sa ma rgyal mtshan gyi rtse mo la btags nas lha'i rnal 'byor dang ldan pas /
T02TD3091E:188a-4: bskor ba dang mchod pa byed cing tshangs pa la sogs pa la mchod pa dang gtor ma sbyin te /
T02TD3091E:188a-5: gsol ba btab na bu 'dod pa nges bu rnyed de tshe dang bsod nams kyi stobs kyang dpag tu med pa yang rnyed do //
T02TD3091E:188a-6: dngos grub bsgrub pa'i thabs rdzogs so//
